textBeforeTable: PAC-12 ALL-ACADEMIC - MEN’S GOLF   WALNUT CREEK, Calif. - Following are the 2014 Pac-12 Conference Men's and Women’s Golf All-Academic teams, announced today by Commissioner Larry Scott. To be eligible for selection to the academic team, a student-athlete must have a minimum 3.0 overall grade point average and be either a starter or significant contributor. May 29, 2014 Pac-12 Conference By Pac-12 names men's and women's golf all-academic teams Pac-12 News
